If a power reading is detected, record reading Then, record that power is on, IF this sensor is live. Otherwise, do nothing.

property.name: text
property.value: An actor that sends mail to If This Then That when a token arrives on the "trigger" input port

property.name: text
property.value:
Replace "to" email address with: trigger@ifttt.com
Replace "from" email address with your address registered on If This Then That
Replace subject and message with content for IFTTT Should include # to activate recipe
Replace SMPTUserName with your username
Create a file containing your password at: $HOME/.mailPassword.txt
IMPORTANT! Right click on SendMail actor -> check "reallySendMail" Check your SPAM folder for mail
Note: enableSSL is checked, as Berkeley mail requires this. Berkeley SMTP info: https://calmail.berkeley.edu/docs/client.html
Gmail SMTP info: http://email.about.com/od/accessinggmail/f/Gmail_SMTP_Settings.htm

property.name: text
